# Aura DESIGN.md

This project includes **DESIGN.md** at the **repository root** (install the spec and this rule together via `pnpm dlx shadcn@latest add @aura/rule-design-md`, or only the markdown via `@aura/design-md`). It is the **narrative design specification** for Aura: visual theme, color roles, typography, the **13px spacing grid**, motion, and product principles.

* **MUST**: When implementing UI, aligning with brand, or reasoning about Aura tokens, read and follow **`DESIGN.md`** at the project root together with `.cursor/rules/*` foundation rules.
* **SHOULD**: Prefer tokens and patterns described in **DESIGN.md** over ad-hoc styling or one-off hex values.
